{"tid":149901,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"DIY 4K SCREEN","createTime":"2017-03-09T15:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-18T17:23:32.000Z","uid":65300,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ea226e6d5c5485d111d0463ea766ceb98c692489","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T15:05:35.000Z","msg":"小弟一直想搵17.3&quot; 4K monitor 但搵極都搵唔到<br />\n睇完youtube<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CfirQC99xPc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DCfirQC99xPc&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=22015fa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CfirQC99xPc</a><br />\n就決定DIY<br />\n暫時睇中左 <a href=\"http://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/17-3-AUO-B173ZAN01-0-4K-UHD-LCD-Screen-Display-Panel-3840x2160-Industrial-Part-/232262297115?hash=item3613e9661b:g:ungAAOSw32lYvX6x\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ebay.co.uk%2Fitm%2F17-3-AUO-B173ZAN01-0-4K-UHD-LCD-Screen-Display-Panel-3840x2160-Industrial-Part-%2F232262297115%3Fhash%3Ditem3613e9661b%3Ag%3AungAAOSw32lYvX6x&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=82bb35e8\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ebay.co.uk/itm/17-3-AUO-B173ZAN01-0-4K-UHD-LCD-Screen-Display-Panel-3840x2160-Industrial-Part-/232262297115?hash=item3613e9661b:g:ungAAOSw32lYvX6x</a><br />\nAUO 17.3&quot; 4K panel <br />\n佢寫就係40 pin edp connector 但搵唔到LCD controller board for AUO B173ZAN01<br />\n<br />\n小弟想請教下各位巴打  我可唔可以是但搵塊有40pin edp connector 既 LCD controller board <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a054484d004da2d9bf1aca3ebf550f55da13cc43","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:11:03.000Z","msg":"幫幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"224573e8f7572671dc88e9943dfdffb2862b8b40","tid":149901,"uid":23890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T16:19:21.000Z","msg":"以前上網睇過 但冇深究過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 入黎推下<br />\n<br />\n好似要對返塊panel個model no. 未必隻隻comtroller都啱洗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"http://www.instructables.com/id/How-to-Convert-a-Laptop-LCD-into-an-External-Monit/step7/Buying-the-LCD-controller-board/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instructables.com%2Fid%2FHow-to-Convert-a-Laptop-LCD-into-an-External-Monit%2Fstep7%2FBuying-the-LCD-controller-board%2F&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6gRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=363b42f7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.instructables.com/id/How-to-Convert-a-Laptop-LCD-into-an-External-Monit/step7/Buying-the-LCD-controller-board/</a>"},{"pid":"e7583cf162bcbf492c194fc10254817dbee68d41","tid":149901,"uid":33059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:04:41.000Z","msg":"咁細行乜4K呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306421368524d5ac15fb8f73e6debfa6af2c2a60","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-09T17:28:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁細行乜4K呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n小弟唔想要大mon 又想要4k 所以自己整  幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e1c95bc0cd0093c2a8a37cbc6796b7ec57767f8","tid":149901,"uid":14230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"