/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢到？</blockquote><br />\n385人仔, 11.6&quot; FHD<br />\n仲有隻15.6&quot; FHD below 5百<br />\n唔好問有無4k<br />\n大陸仔最多都係得FHD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淘寶controller board keyword係咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88d2c6ff9aefaac09c3fd7b3172f380315dffe90","tid":149901,"uid":1066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-11T08:52:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>係淘仔訂左個11.6連control panel<br />\n(15.6羅出街唔方便 同我掛床個mount最大食到13&quot;)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等緊到<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾錢到？</blockquote><br />\n385人仔, 11.6&quot; FHD<br />\n仲有隻15.6&quot; FHD below 5百<br />\n唔好問有無4k<br />\n大陸仔最多都係得FHD<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n淘寶controller board keyword係咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你試下直接打panel 名 or &quot;高清HDMI驱动板显示器&quot;<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8be41e1ea1f171a965bd49257b87be10fba074f7","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T00:55:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>買個大moon啊<br />\n我都買左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n打機睇戲都爽D<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申英撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都想大mon 但真係無位<br />\n同埋原本個mon 係17吋 用左十年 慣晒啦<br />\n加上laptop 14吋 usb mon 15.6. 真係唔想大mon"},{"pid":"e7b55a11f5f66ea716314a8c48c07b2d1914347f","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T01:00:47.000Z","msg":"家下ebay有人賣DP board. <br />\n以下4k panel都支援<br />\nLP156UD1<br />\nLTN156FL02<br />\nB173ZAN01.0<br />\n要再研究下eDP 同 LVDS 頭有咩分別<br />\n以上3隻mon都係eDP<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有大陸仔ebay 4k panel + dp board 一次過賣  但我信唔過  board預左強國貨  <br />\nmon 一定要英國代理貨（雖然都係made in chi na）<br />\n主因係比少d import tax<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d22b824df14ffc12e0b13e15e7dfcaf61e6d040","tid":149901,"uid":37097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T05:11:24.000Z","msg":"Edp 新過lvds, 高清mon 多數行edp<br />\n近幾代intel 內置display 都cut 左lvds, 得番edp"},{"pid":"cb63b65f9c8b7ef0b8201fa4e577f8df83df454b","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-13T16:27:26.000Z","msg":"搵到driver board <br />\n又support 4k panel<br />\n但佢竟然唔賣埋條connect cable<br />\n我又唔知佢用咩interface<br />\n搞到我咩都未買得<br />\n佢圖就寫edp output <br />\n但我睇資料就係lvds 30 pin <br />\n亂到我呢<br />\n有無其他高手教教我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2bad71ff3f0b0efdff21fc9280b64d8688309e6","tid":149901,"uid":1066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T13:25:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9YscnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv9YscnL.jpg&h=d1aecd64&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qM470nS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqM470nS.jpg&h=e9fa68f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n4百幾 samsung 味mon 無伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0adb751c158343a6361099e0cfe313daa5ac847a","tid":149901,"uid":65300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-18T16:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v9YscnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn